<thead>
<tr>
<th>Ranking Factor</th>
<th>Weight</th>
<th>What It Means</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>Content-Answer Fit</td>
<td>55%</td>
<td>How closely your content matches the answer ChatGPT wants to give</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>On-Page Structure</td>
<td>14%</td>
<td>Logical H2/H3 hierarchy, balanced section lengths, parseable formatting</td>
</tr>
<tr>
